        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-2">
          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center rounded-3 px-3 py-2 welcome-stat-row">
            <span class="text-muted">Email Encryption</span>
            <span class="badge text-bg-success">AES</span>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center rounded-3 px-3 py-2 welcome-stat-row">
            <span class="text-muted">Claim Integrity</span>
            <span class="badge text-bg-primary">SHA-256</span>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center rounded-3 px-3 py-2 welcome-stat-row">
