      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="welcome-step-card p-3 h-100 rounded-4 reveal-on-scroll">
          <span class="welcome-step-index">01</span>
          <i class="bi bi-person-vcard fs-2 text-primary d-block mb-2"></i>
          <h5 class="fw-bold">Secure Registration</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Create an account and upload your identity proof. Sensitive data remains encrypted.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="welcome-step-card p-3 h-100 rounded-4 reveal-on-scroll">
          <span class="welcome-step-index">02</span>
          <i class="bi bi-patch-check fs-2 text-primary d-block mb-2"></i>
          <h5 class="fw-bold">Claim Verification</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Admin verifies your claim so the platform can validate trust without leaking identity details.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="welcome-step-card p-3 h-100 rounded-4 reveal-on-scroll">
          <span class="welcome-step-index">03</span>
          <i class="bi bi-qr-code-scan fs-2 text-primary d-block mb-2"></i>
          <h5 class="fw-bold">Temporary Proof Sharing</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Generate a short-lived code and QR only when needed for live verification checks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="row g-4 mb-4 mb-lg-5">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <div class="surface-card p-4 h-100 reveal-on-scroll">
        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Built for privacy-sensitive use cases</h4>
        <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0 d-flex flex-column gap-2">
          <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>Campus and enterprise access checks</li>
          <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>KYC-lite flows for platform onboarding</li>
          <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>Minimal-data identity attestation</li>
          <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>Time-bound verification events</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <div class="surface-card p-4 h-100 reveal-on-scroll">
        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Why this approach matters</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-0">
          Traditional systems collect and expose too much personal information. Privia keeps verification focused on
          trusted claims and temporary proofs so users stay in control of what is revealed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="surface-card p-4 p-lg-5 mb-4 mb-lg-5 reveal-on-scroll">
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">Why users trust Privia</h3>
        <div class="accordion" id="privacyAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-item border-0 mb-2 rounded-3 overflow-hidden">
            <h2 class="accordion-header">
              <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne">
                Data minimization by default
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#privacyAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                Verification checks are based on cryptographic claims instead of exposing full personal records.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item border-0 mb-2 rounded-3 overflow-hidden">
            <h2 class="accordion-header">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo">
                Fast, temporary proof exchange
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#privacyAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                Time-limited QR proofs reduce replay risk and keep each verification tied to a short trusted window.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item border-0 rounded-3 overflow-hidden">
            <h2 class="accordion-header">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree">
                Human oversight with admin checks
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#privacyAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                Claims are approved by admins before users can present verification proofs in downstream workflows.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="surface-card p-4 h-100 border-0 welcome-interactive-panel">
          <h4 class="fw-bold mb-2">Live Verification Experience</h4>
          <p class="text-muted mb-3">
            A verifier scans a QR code and receives a binary result: valid, expired, or not verified. No sensitive data leak.
          </p>
          <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-2">
            <div class="welcome-flow-chip"><i class="bi bi-1-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i>User generates proof</div>
            <div class="welcome-flow-chip"><i class="bi bi-2-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i>QR scanned by verifier</div>
            <div class="welcome-flow-chip"><i class="bi bi-3-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i>Backend validates expiry + status</div>
            <div class="welcome-flow-chip"><i class="bi bi-4-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i>Instant trust decision</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="surface-card p-4 p-lg-5 text-center welcome-cta reveal-on-scroll">
    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2">Trust should be provable, not invasive.</h2>
    <p class="text-muted mb-4">Bring secure, privacy-preserving identity verification into your workflow today.</p>
    <% if (!user) { %>
      <a href="/users/register" class="btn btn-lg btn-privia px-4">Create Your Privia Account</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-lg btn-privia px-4">Go to Dashboard</a>
        <% } %>
  </section>
</div>

<script>
  (() => {
    const revealItems = document.querySelectorAll(".reveal-on-scroll");
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add("revealed");
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.15 });

    revealItems.forEach((item) => observer.observe(item));

    const counters = document.querySelectorAll(".count-up");
    counters.forEach((counter) => {
      const target = Number(counter.dataset.count || 0);
      let current = 0;
      const step = Math.max(1, Math.ceil(target / 24));
      const timer = setInterval(() => {
        current += step;
        if (current >= target) {
          counter.textContent = String(target);
          clearInterval(timer);
          return;
        }
        counter.textContent = String(current);
      }, 35);
    });
  })();
</script>

